<lyrics>[V1]
 mḥtqr wmkẖtbr ạlḥzn hw yswʿ lạ swạh
 nḥsbh mṣạbaⁿạ mdẖlwlaⁿạ ạ̉w mḍrwbaⁿạ mn ạlạ̹lh
 mjrwḥ mn ạ̉jl ạlmʿạṣy msḥwq mn ạ̉jl ạlạ̉tẖạm
 slạmnạ bh yūảdãbu ḥbwrh tsẖfy ạlsqạm
 kgẖnm ḍllnạ ạlkl mạl fy ạlṭryq
 ạ̹tẖm jmyʿnạ ʿlyh fy qlbh ḥzn ʿmyq
 ạ̉mạ hw fqd tdẖll fy ṣmth lm yftḥ fạh
 knʿjẗ ạ̉mạm ạljạzyn lldẖbḥ sạr mtẖl sẖạẗ
 lknh ẓlmaⁿạ lạ yrtkb bl kạn hạdyaⁿ̉ạ wdyʿ
 wạlgẖsẖ lm ykn fy fmh bl jạl ybrỷ ạljmyʿ</lyrics>
<title>mḥtqr wmkẖtbr</title>
</song>